Championship.Name: Division 1 | Season 4 | GT3 Team Championship
Championship.Description:
RACE FORMAT

Driver Briefing To Start at 8:50PM (Mandatory)

• Free Practice: 5 minutes (Will advance right at 9PM to quali)

• Qualifying: 30 Mins, (15 Mins for silver, 15 mins for gold) 

• Race: 60 minutes

 One mandatory pit stop - Fixed pit window; 

 During the pit stop every driver must add at least 1 litre of fuel;

 Tyres and fuel strategy are not subject to any restrictions;

 Pit Window duration: 10 minutes;

 Pit Window opens after 25 minutes from the start of the race.

BALANCE OF PERFORMANCE

The organizer reserves the right to apply a custom Manufacturer Balance of Performance.


You'll be racing your own car and race number. Your number does NOT need to your teammate's number.  Only the cars need to match.
